  "prompt": "Which Bluetooth speakers are the best for under Rs 5k?",
  "response": "As of October 2023, there are several good Bluetooth speakers available under Rs 5,000 in India. Here are some popular options that offer great sound quality, portability, and battery life:\n\n1. **JBL Flip 5**:\n   - Known for its powerful sound and bass.\n   - IPX7 waterproof rating.\n   - Good battery life of around 12 hours.\n\n2. **Boat Stone 1000**:\n   - Rugged design with IPX7 water resistance.\n   - Decent sound quality and powerful bass.\n   - Battery life of around 10 hours.\n\n3. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush**:\n   - Stylish design with RGB lights.\n   - Dual 10W speakers for enhanced sound.\n   - Built-in FM radio and good battery life.\n\n4. **Sony SRS-XB01**:\n   - Compact size with Extra Bass feature.\n   - Water-resistant design (IP67).\n   - Battery life of around 16 hours.\n\n5. **Mi Portable Bluetooth Speaker**:\n   - Clear sound quality with good volume.\n   - 20-hour battery backup.\n   - Supports voice assistant.\n\n6. **Ambrane BT-560**:\n   - Good sound quality for its price.\n   - Built-in FM Radio and supports microSD.\n   - Decent battery life.\n\n7. **Infinity (JBL) Fuze 100**:\n   - Dual Equalizer Modes for enhanced audio experience.\n   - IPX7 waterproof rating.\n   - Up to 12 hours of playback time.\n\n8. **Portronics BANG BANG P-100**:\n   - Compact and lightweight design.\n   - Good sound quality with a solid bass response.\n   - Features Bluetooth and AUX connectivity.\n\nWhen selecting a Bluetooth speaker, consider your specific needs such as sound quality, battery life, portability, and any additional features like water resistance or built-in FM radio. Prices may vary, so it's a good idea to check online platforms for the best deals and specifications.",
